'''小泉八云纪念馆'''（{{lang-en|Lafcadio Hearn Memorial Museum}}）是一座位于[[日本|日本]][[岛根县|岛根县]][[松江市|松江市]]的博物馆。 

==历史==
1934年6月建成开馆。纪念日本作家[[小泉八云|小泉八云]]的博物馆，2016年4月其曾孙[[小泉凡|小泉凡]]担任馆长。<ref>{{cite news|title=「これ以上の適任いない」と松江市　小泉八雲記念館長にハーンの曽孫が就任|url=https://www.sankei.com/west/news/160401/wst1604010075-n1.html|newspaper=[[産経新聞|産経新聞]]|publisher=株式会社産経デジタル|date=2016-04-01|accessdate=2019-10-28|archive-date=2019-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191028105136/https://www.sankei.com/west/news/160401/wst1604010075-n1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>每年约有15万游客参观。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bunka.nii.ac.jp/SearchDetail.do?heritageId=162048 |title=Lafcadio Hearn's Former Residence |publisher=[[Agency_for_Cultural_Affairs|Agency for Cultural Affairs]] |accessdate=31 January 2012 |archive-date=2012-07-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707011142/http://bunka.nii.ac.jp/SearchDetail.do?heritageId=162048 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.matsue-tourism.or.jp/yakumo/page02.html |title=Lafcadio Hearn Memorial Museum |publisher=Matsue Tourism Board |accessdate=31 January 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130111092422/http://www.matsue-tourism.or.jp/yakumo/page02.html |archivedate=11 January 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/museumstudies/museumsociety/documents/volumes/askew.pdf |title=The politics of nostalgia: museum representations of Lafcadio Hearn in Japan |author=Askew, Rie Kido |journal=Museum and Society |publisher=[[University_of_Leicester|University of Leicester]] |volume=5 |number=3 |year=2007 |pages=131–147 |access-date=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2016-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311162739/https://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/museumstudies/museumsociety/documents/volumes/askew.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

